  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "横綱物語は、スーパーファミコン用の相撲マネジメントシミュレーションゲームです。相撲力士の育成や対戦の設定を通じて、ランキングを向上させる管理要素に焦点を当てています。相撲の試合でお金を稼ぐことで、プレイヤーはより強力な力士を雇うことができるようになりますが、彼らは当然、より多くの報酬を要求します。目標は、相撲力士を横綱（「大関」）のレベルに育て上げることです。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "Yokozuna Monogatari is a Sports game, published by KSS, which was released in Japan in 1994.\n\nYokozuna Monogatari is a sumo game for the Super Famicom. It focuses on management aspects, training sumo wrestlers and setting up bouts to improve their ranking. Earning money from sumo matches allows the player to hire stronger wrestlers, who naturally ask for more money to be recruited. The goal is to train a sumo wrestler to Yokozuna (\"Grand Champion\") level.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    }
  ],
  "first_release_date": "1994-08-26",
